a:18:{s:4:"name";s:8:"Cafergot";s:11:"small_descr";s:94:"Cafergot (Caffeine/Ergotamine) is used for preventing and treating certain kinds of headaches.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:170:"Cafergot wird zur Behandlung von Anfällen Migräneartiger Kopfschmerzen (z.B. Migräne mit und ohne Aura, Kopfschmerzen durch Einwirkung von Histaminstoffen) verwendet. ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:158:"Cafergot est utilisé pour prévenir et traiter certains types de maux de tête (par exemple, la migraine,des variantes de migraine, "le syndrome de Horton").";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:161:"Cafergot es utilizado para prevenir y tratar ciertos tipos de dolores de cabeza (por ejemplo, las migrañas, las variantes de migrañas, "cefalea histamínica").";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:120:"Cafergot si usa per prevenire e trattare alcuni tipi del mal di testa (per esempio emicranie, 'histaminic cephalalgia').";s:10:"full_descr";s:4882:"<p><strong>Drug Name</strong><br /><br />Cafergot (Caffeine/Ergotamine)&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Drug Uses</strong><br /><br />Cafergot is used for preventing and treating certain kinds of headaches (e.g., migraines, migraine variants, histaminic cephalalgia). It may also be used for other conditions as determined by your doctor.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>How to use</strong><br /><br />Use Cafergot as directed by your doctor.&nbsp;<br /> Cafergot may be taken with or without food. <br /> Eating grapefruit or drinking grapefruit juice may affect the amount of Cafergot in your blood. Talk with your doctor before including grapefruit or grapefruit juice in your diet. <br /> Cafergot is only to be used as needed for a migraine attack. <br /> Take Cafergot at the first sign of a headache. If the initial dose does not relieve your headache, additional doses may be needed according to your doctor's instructions. Do not take a dose of Cafergot within 30 minutes of your last dose. <br />Do not take more than 6 tablets for a single migraine headache or more than 10 tablets during any 7-day period without first checking with your doctor. <br /> Ask your health care provider any questions you may have about how to use Cafergot. <br /><br /><strong>Drug Class and Mechanism</strong><br /><br />Cafergot is a combination of 2 vasoconstrictors. It works by constricting blood vessels in the lining of the brain, which helps to decrease the pain from migraine headaches.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Missed Dose</strong><br /><br />If you miss a dose of Cafergot and you still have a headache, take it as soon as you remember. Do not take a dose of Cafergot within 30 minutes of your last dose. Do not take 2 doses at once.&nbsp;<br />Storage<br /><br />Store Cafergot at room temperature, between 68 and 77 degrees F (20 and 25 degrees C). Store away from heat, moisture, and light. Keep Cafergot out of the reach of children and away from pets.</p><p><strong>Warnings/Precautions</strong><br /><br />Do not use Cafergot if:&nbsp;<br /> you are allergic to any ingredient in Cafergot. <br /> you are pregnant or may become pregnant. <br /> you have blood vessel problems (e.g., peripheral vascular disease), coronary heart disease, high blood pressure, liver or kidney problems, or severe infection (e.g., sepsis). <br /> you are taking an azole antifungal (e.g., itraconazole, ketoconazole, voriconazole), delavirdine, HIV protease inhibitors (e.g., delavirdine, indinavir, nelfinavir, ritonavir), efavirenz, a ketolide antibiotic (e.g., telithromycin), a macrolide antibiotic (e.g., clarithromycin, erythromycin), or selective 5-HT agonists (e.g., sumatriptan, eletriptan). <br /> Contact your doctor or health care provider right away if any of these apply to you. <br /><br /> <strong>Important:&nbsp;<br /></strong><strong></strong><br /> Do not exceed the recommended dose or take Cafergot for longer than prescribed without checking with your doctor. Cafergot is not for long-term daily use. <br /> Do not take Cafergot for any other kind of headaches. Cafergot is not effective in treating other types of headaches. <br /> Use of nicotine may increase the risk of severe side effects with Cafergot . Talk to you doctor before using Cafergot if you smoke or use any other kind of nicotine. <br /> Use Cafergot with extreme caution in children. Safety and effectiveness have not been confirmed. <br /> Pregnancy and breast-feeding: Do not use Cafergot if you are pregnant. If you suspect that you could be pregnant, contact your doctor immediately. Cafergot should not be taken during labor and delivery. Cafergot is excreted in breast milk. If you are or will be breast-feeding while you are using Cafergot , check with your doctor or pharmacist to discuss the risks to your baby.</p><p><strong>Possible Side Effects</strong><br /><br />Check with your doctor if any of these most common side effects persist or become bothersome:&nbsp;<br /> nausea. <br /> Seek medical attention right away if any of these severe side effects occur: <br /><br /> severe allergic reactions (rash; hives; itching; difficulty breathing; tightness in the chest; swelling of the mouth, face, lips, or tongue); blue color of the fingers or toes; chest pain or tightness; cold or pale fingers or toes; diarrhea; dizziness; hallucinations; headache; irregular heartbeat; leg cramps or weakness; mental or mood changes; muscle pain; numbness or tingling of the hands, feet, or skin; ringing in the ears; seizure; severe or persistent nausea or vomiting; shortness of breath; swelling; temporary fast or slow heartbeat; vomiting; weak pulse. <br /><br /><strong>More Information</strong><br /><br />Cafergot is to be used only by the patient for whom it is prescribed. Do not share it with other people.&nbsp;<br /> If your symptoms do not improve or if they become worse, check with your doctor.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:22309:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">est</span> <span class="hps">indiqu&eacute; pour le traitement</span> <span class="hps">ou la</span> <span class="hps">pr&eacute;vention</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des maux de t&ecirc;te</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">vasculaires</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">par exemple</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la migraine, </span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des variantes de migraine</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps">que l'on </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">appelle</span> <span class="hps atn">"</span><span class="alt-edited">la c&eacute;phalalgie</span> <span class="hps">histaminique</span><span>.</span><span>"</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">est une combinaison de</span> <span class="hps">2</span> <span class="hps">vasoconstricteurs</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Il fonctionne en</span> <span class="hps">r&eacute;tr&eacute;cissant les vaisseaux</span> <span class="hps">sanguins dans les parois</span> <span class="hps">du cerveau</span><span>, ce qui</span> <span class="hps">aide &agrave; r&eacute;duire la</span> <span class="hps">douleur provenant des migraines</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong>A</strong><strong>DMINISTRATION</strong></p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">comme est indiqu&eacute; par votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span></span></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">peut &ecirc;tre pris avec</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou sans aliment</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne</span> <span class="hps">mangez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le pamplemousse</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou ne buvez pas de jus</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de pamplemousse, ce</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peut affecter</span> <span class="hps">la quantit&eacute; de</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">dans votre sang.</span> <span class="hps">Discutez avec votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">avant d'inclure</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le pamplemousse ou de jus</span> <span class="hps">de pamplemousse</span> <span class="hps">dans votre r&eacute;gime alimentaire</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">doit &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">selon les besoin</span> <span class="hps">pour</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le traitement de la crise de migraine</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Prenez</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">au premier signe</span> <span class="hps">d'un</span> <span class="hps">mal de t&ecirc;te.</span> <span class="hps">Si la dose initiale</span> <span class="hps">ne soulage pas votre</span> <span class="hps">mal de t&ecirc;te,</span> <span class="hps">des doses</span> <span class="hps">suppl&eacute;mentaires peuvent &ecirc;tre n&eacute;cessaires</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">selon </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">les conseils</span> <span class="hps">de votre m&eacute;decin.</span> <span class="hps">Ne prenez pas</span> <span class="hps">une dose de</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">dans les 30</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">minutes apr&egrave;s votre</span> <span class="hps">derni&egrave;re dose</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">prenez pas plus que</span> <span class="hps">6 comprim&eacute;s pour</span> <span class="hps">soulager une migraine</span> <span class="hps">seule</span> <span class="hps">ou plus de 10</span> <span class="hps">comprim&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">au cours d'une</span> <span class="hps">p&eacute;riode de 7 jours</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">sans v&eacute;rification</span> <span class="hps">avec votre m&eacute;decin.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">manquez une dose de</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">et vous avez toujours</span> <span class="hps">un mal de t&ecirc;te</span> <span class="hps">prenez-la d&egrave;s</span> <span class="hps">que vous vous souvenez</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Ne prenez pas</span> <span class="hps">une dose de</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">dans </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">les 30</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">minutes apr&egrave;s votre</span> <span class="hps">derni&egrave;re dose</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Ne prenez pas 2</span> <span class="hps">doses &agrave; la fois</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Si vous avez des questions sur l'utilisation de <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot, </span></span>contactez votre m&eacute;decin<span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">.</span></span></p><p><strong>CONSERVATION</strong></p><p>Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot</span> </span>&agrave; la temp&eacute;rature ambiante, entre 59 et 86 degr&eacute;s F (15 et 30 degr&eacute;s C). Entreposez loin de la chaleur et l'humidit&eacute; dans une bo&icirc;te ferm&eacute;e, r&eacute;sistante &agrave; la lumi&egrave;re. Ne le gardez pas dans la salle de bain. Gardez <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot </span></span>hors de la port&eacute;e des enfants et loin des animaux.</p><p><strong>INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</strong><br /><br />L'ingr&eacute;dient actif: <span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Tartrate d'Ergotamine et</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">Caf&eacute;ine</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong>N'utilisez pas Cafergot si:</strong></p><ul><li>vous &ecirc;tes allergique &agrave; un ingr&eacute;dient de Cafergot</li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous &ecirc;tes enceinte ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pouvez devenir enceinte</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&ecirc;tes en couches</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous avez des probl&egrave;mes</span> <span class="hps atn">de vaisseaux sanguins (</span><span>par exemple</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la maladie vasculaire p&eacute;riph&eacute;rique)</span><span class="alt-edited">, la maladie coronarienne</span><span>, l'hypertension art&eacute;rielle</span><span>, des probl&egrave;mes de</span> <span class="hps">foie ou des reins</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou une infection</span> <span class="hps">grave (p. ex</span><span>, la septic&eacute;mie</span><span>)</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">vous prenez</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">un antifongique de type azole</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span>, itraconazole,</span> <span class="hps">k&eacute;toconazole, voriconazole</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">delavirdine</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">les inhibiteurs de prot&eacute;ase</span> <span class="hps">du VIH</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="alt-edited">delavirdine</span><span class="alt-edited">, indinavir</span><span>, nelfinavir, ritonavir</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&eacute;favirenz</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">un antibiotique de</span> <span class="hps">ketolide</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, t&eacute;lithromycine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">un antibiotique macrolide</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">clarithromycine</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;rythromycine) ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les agonistes s&eacute;lectifs de 5-HT </span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, sumatriptan</span><span class="alt-edited">, &eacute;l&eacute;triptan</span><span>)</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Contactez votre m&eacute;decin imm&eacute;diatement si l'un de ces cas s'applique &agrave; vous.</p><p>Certaines  conditions m&eacute;dicales peuvent interagir avec Cafergot.  Informez votre  m&eacute;decin ou votre pharmacien si vous avez des conditions  m&eacute;dicales,  surtout si une des conditions suivantes s'applique &agrave; vous:</p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous</span> <span class="hps">envisagez de devenir</span> <span class="hps">enceinte ou</span> <span class="hps">allaitez</span></span></li><li>si vous prenez une ordonnance ou un m&eacute;dicament en vente libre, une pr&eacute;paration d'herbes ou un suppl&eacute;ment alimentaire</li><li>si vous avez des allergies aux m&eacute;dicaments, aliments ou autres substances</li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous avez</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des probl&egrave;mes</span> <span class="hps">sanguins</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span>, la porphyrie</span><span class="alt-edited">),</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'accident vasculaire c&eacute;r&eacute;bral,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'anxi&eacute;t&eacute;</span><span class="alt-edited">, les troubles du sommeil</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou les probl&egrave;mes du c&oelig;ur</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">si vous fumez</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Certains m&eacute;dicaments peuvent interagir avec Cafergot. Informez votre   m&eacute;decin si vous prenez d'autres m&eacute;dicaments, en particulier les &eacute;l&eacute;ments   suivants:</p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Clotrimazole, fluconazole</span><span class="alt-edited">, fluox&eacute;tine</span><span class="alt-edited">, fluvoxamine,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited"> m&eacute;tronidazole</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">n&eacute;fazodone</span><span class="alt-edited">, saquinavir,</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps">zileuton</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">car les effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;tre augment&eacute;s</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Les antifongiques de type azole</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span>, itraconazole,</span> <span class="hps">k&eacute;toconazole, voriconazole</span><span>), les b&ecirc;ta</span><span>-bloquants</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, propranolol)</span><span class="alt-edited">, delavirdine</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">les inhibiteurs de prot&eacute;ase</span> <span class="hps">du VIH</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, delavirdine</span><span class="alt-edited">, indinavir</span><span>, nelfinavir, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span>ritonavir</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&eacute;favirenz</span><span>, les antibiotiques</span> <span class="hps">k&eacute;tolides</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, t&eacute;lithromycine</span><span>)</span><span>, les antibiotiques macrolides</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, &eacute;rythromycine</span><span class="alt-edited">, clarithromycine</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les agonistes s&eacute;lectifs de 5-HT </span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, sumatriptan</span><span class="alt-edited">, &eacute;l&eacute;triptan</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">parce que le </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">risque d'effets</span> <span class="hps">secondaires graves</span><span class="alt-edited">, y compris le</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">rythme cardiaque irr&eacute;gulier</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou la baisse</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">d'acc&egrave;s d'oxyg&egrave;ne aux extr&eacute;mit&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">(les mains</span><span class="alt-edited">, les pieds</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">ou le cerveau</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peut &ecirc;tre</span> <span class="hps">augment&eacute;</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">Des vasopresseurs</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, norepinephrine</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">des sympathomim&eacute;tiques</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, pseudo&eacute;ph&eacute;drine</span><span>, salbutamol</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">en raison</span> <span class="hps">du risque</span> <span class="hps">d'effets secondaires</span><span>, y compris</span> <span class="hps">l'hypertension art&eacute;rielle s&eacute;v&egrave;re</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;tre augment&eacute;s</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Les quinolones</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, l&eacute;vofloxacinetiques</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, pseudo</span><span>, salbutamol</span><span>)</span> <span class="hps">en raison</span> <span class="hps">du risque</span> <span class="hps">d'effets secondaires</span><span>, y compris</span> <span class="hps">l'hypertension art&eacute;</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Les quinolones</span> <span class="hps">(par exemple</span><span class="alt-edited">, l&eacute;</span><span>)</span><span>, car le risque</span> <span class="hps">d'effets secondaires,</span> <span class="hps">tels que la nervosit&eacute;</span><span>, l'insomnie et</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le battement de coeur rapide</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">peuvent &ecirc;tre augment&eacute;s</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Th&eacute;ophylline</span> <span class="hps">parce que les actions</span> <span class="hps">et les effets</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">secondaires peuvent &ecirc;tre augment&eacute;s</span> <span class="hps">par</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span><span>.</span></span></li></ul><p>Ce n'est pas une liste compl&egrave;te de toutes les interactions qui  peuvent  se produire. Demandez &agrave; votre m&eacute;decin si Cafergot peut  interagir avec  d'autres m&eacute;dicaments que vous prenez. V&eacute;rifiez aupr&egrave;s de  votre  pharmacien avant de commencer, arr&ecirc;ter ou modifier la dose de  tout  m&eacute;dicament.</p><p><strong>Information de s&eacute;curit&eacute; importante:</strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">N'utilisez pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">plus que la dose recommand&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou </span> <span class="hps">plus longtemps</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">que prescrit sans</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">consultation avec votre m&eacute;decin</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ne doit pas etre utilis&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; long terme.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">L'utilisation de</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">nicotine</span> <span class="hps">peut augmenter</span> <span class="hps">le risque d'effets</span> <span class="hps">ind&eacute;sirables graves</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Parlez-en &agrave;</span> <span class="hps">votre m&eacute;decin</span> <span class="hps">avant d'utiliser</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">si vous fumez</span> <span class="hps">ou utilisez</span> <span class="hps">un autre type</span> <span class="hps">de nicotine</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">avec une extr&ecirc;me prudence</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">aux enfants</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">La s&eacute;curit&eacute; et l'efficacit&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">n'ont pas &eacute;t&eacute; confirm&eacute;es</span><span>.</span></span></li><li><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">La grossesse</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">et l'allaitement</span><span>:</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">N'utilisez pas</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">si vous &ecirc;tes enceinte</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si vous</span> <span class="hps">pensez que vous pourriez</span> <span class="hps">&ecirc;tre enceinte</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">contactez imm&eacute;diatement votre m&eacute;decin</span><span>. </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ne doit pas &ecirc;tre pris</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pendant l'accouchement.</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">est excr&eacute;t&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">dans le lait maternel</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Si vous &ecirc;tes ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">serez</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">allaiter pendant que</span> <span class="hps">vous utilisez</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span><span>, v&eacute;rifiez avec votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin ou votre pharmacien</span> <span class="hps">pour discuter des risques</span> <span class="hps">&agrave; votre </span></span><br /><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">b&eacute;b&eacute;.</span></span></li></ul><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Lorsqu'il est utilis&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">pendant de longues p&eacute;riodes</span> <span class="hps">de temps ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">aux doses &eacute;lev&eacute;es</span><span>, certaines personnes</span> <span class="hps">&eacute;prouvent le besoin de</span> <span class="hps">continuer &agrave; prendre</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Ceci </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">est connu comme</span> <span class="hps">la d&eacute;pendance</span> <span class="hps">ou la toxicomanie</span><span>.</span> <span class="hps">Il est</span> <span class="hps">important que vous preniez</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">comme indiqu&eacute; par votre</span> <span class="hps">m&eacute;decin.</span> <span class="hps">Cafergot</span> <span class="hps">n'est pas</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">pour </span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'utilisation quotidienne de longue dur&eacute;e</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong>LES EFFETS SECONDAIRES</strong></p><p>Tout les m&eacute;dicaments peuvent causer des effets secondaires, mais   beaucoup de gens n'ont pas, ou ont des effets secondaires mineurs.</p><p>Consultez votre m&eacute;decin si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables persiste ou devient g&ecirc;nant:</p><p>La <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">naus&eacute;e.</span></span></p><p>Consultez un m&eacute;decin imm&eacute;diatement si l'un de ces effets ind&eacute;sirables s&eacute;v&egrave;res se produit:</p><p>Les r&eacute;actions allergiques graves (l'&eacute;ruption cutan&eacute;e, l'urticaire, la   d&eacute;mangeaison, la difficult&eacute; &agrave; respirer, la sensation d'oppression dans   la poitrine, l'enflure de la bouche, du visage, des l&egrave;vres ou de la   langue), <span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">la couleur bleue les</span> <span class="hps">doigts ou les orteils,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la douleur ou l'oppression dans la poitrine,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les doigts ou les orteils froids</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou p&acirc;les, </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">la diarrh&eacute;e, l'&eacute;tourdissement,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les hallucinations</span><span class="alt-edited">, les maux de t&ecirc;te</span><span class="alt-edited">, le rythme cardiaque</span> <span class="hps">irr&eacute;gulier,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">les crampes aux jambes</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ou la faiblesse</span><span>, les changements</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de mentalit&eacute; ou d'humeur</span><span class="alt-edited">, les douleurs</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">musculaires, l'engourdissement</span> <span class="hps">ou</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">le </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps alt-edited">picotement dans les</span> <span class="hps">mains, les pieds</span> <span class="hps">ou la peau</span><span class="alt-edited">, le bourdonnement dans les</span> <span class="hps">oreilles</span><span class="alt-edited">,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">une crise,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">la naus&eacute;e ou le vomissement s&eacute;v&egrave;re ou persistant</span><span class="alt-edited">,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'essoufflement,</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">un gonflement</span></span></p>";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:8810:"<p><strong>INDICACIONES</strong></p><p>Cafergot es indicado como terapia para interrumpir o prevenir dolor de cabeza vascular, por ejemplo, la migra&ntilde;a, las variantes de migra&ntilde;a, o una enfermedad llamada "cefalea histam&iacute;nica." Cafergot es una combinaci&oacute;n de 2 vasoconstrictores. Cafergot estrecha los vasos sangu&iacute;neos en el revestimiento del cerebro, que ayuda a disminuir el dolor de la migra&ntilde;a.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCCIONES</strong></p><p>Use Cafergot como es recetado por el m&eacute;dico.</p><ul><li><span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="es"><span class="hps">Usted puede tomar </span></span>Cafergot <span id="result_box" class="short_text" lang="es"><span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">sin comida.</span></span></li><li> La toronja o el jugo de toronja puede afectar la cantidad de Cafergot en la sangre. Consulte con su m&eacute;dico antes de incluir toronja o jugo de toronja en su dieta.</li><li>Cafergot es solamente para el uso cuando es necesario para un ataque de migra&ntilde;a.</li><li>Tome Cafergot a la primera se&ntilde;al de un dolor de cabeza. Si la dosis inicial no alivia el dolor de cabeza, las dosis adicionales pueden ser necesarios seg&uacute;n las instrucciones del m&eacute;dico. No tome una dosis de Cafergot dentro de los 30 minutos de su &uacute;ltima dosis.</li><li>No tome m&aacute;s de 6 pastillas para una migra&ntilde;a sola o m&aacute;s de 10 tabletas durante cualquier per&iacute;odo de 7 d&iacute;as sin consultar primeramente con el m&eacute;dico.</li><li>Si usted olvida una dosis de Cafergot pero tiene el dolor de cabeza, t&oacute;mela tan pronto como Usted recuerde. No tome una dosis de Cafergot dentro de los 30 minutos de su &uacute;ltima dosis. No tome 2 dosis al mismo tiempo.</li></ul><p>Contacte con su m&eacute;dico si Usted tiene cualquiera pregunta sobre la toma de Cafergot.</p><p><strong>ALMACENAMIENTO </strong><br /><br />Almacene Cafergot a temperatura ambiente entre 59 y 86 grados F (15 y 30 grados C), en un contenedor apretado y resistente a la luz. Almacene lejos del calor, de la humedad y de la luz. No lo guarde en el ba&ntilde;o. Mantiena Cafergot lejos del alcance de los ni&ntilde;os y animales dom&eacute;sticos.</p><p><strong>M&Aacute;S INFORMACI&Oacute;N: </strong><br /><br />Ingredientes activos: Tartrato de ergotamina y cafe&iacute;na.</p><p><strong>INFORMACI&Oacute;N DE SEGURIDAD</strong></p><p><strong>NO use Cafergot si:</strong></p><ul><li>Usted es al&eacute;rgico a cualquier ingrediente de Cafergot</li><li>Usted est&aacute; embarazada o puede caer embarazada</li><li>Usted est&aacute; de parto</li><li>tiene problemas de los vasos sangu&iacute;neos (por ejemplo, enfermedad vascular perif&eacute;rica), enfermedad card&iacute;aca coronaria, presi&oacute;n arterial alta, problemas del h&iacute;gado o del ri&ntilde;&oacute;n, o una infecci&oacute;n grave (por ejemplo, sepsis)</li><li>Usted toma un producto antimic&oacute;tico de azol (por ejemplo, itraconazol, ketoconazol, voriconazol), delavirdina, inhibidores de la proteasa del VIH (por ejemplo, delavirdina, indinavir, nelfinavir, ritonavir), efavirenz, un antibi&oacute;tico cet&oacute;lido (por ejemplo, telitromicina), un antibi&oacute;tico macr&oacute;lido (por ejemplo, claritromicina, eritromicina), o agonistas selectivos de 5-HT (por ejemplo, sumatript&aacute;n, eletript&aacute;n).</li></ul><p>Contacte con su m&eacute;dico inmediatamente si alguna de estas condici&oacute;nes se aplique a Usted.<br /><br />Algunas condiciones m&eacute;dicas pueden interactuar con Cafergot. D&iacute;ga a su m&eacute;dico o farmac&eacute;utico si tiene algunas de las siguientes condici&oacute;nes m&eacute;dicas:</p><ul><li>si planea caer embarazada o amamanta</li><li>si toma cualquier medicamento recetado o medicamento sin receta, preparado herb&aacute;ceo o suplemento diet&eacute;tico</li><li>si usted tiene alergias a medicamentos, alimentos o otras sustancias</li><li>si Usted tiene antecedentes de problemas de la sangre (por ejemplo, la porfiria), ataque cerebral, problemas de ansiedad, dificultad para dormir, o problemas de coraz&oacute;n</li><li>si Usted fuma.</li></ul><p>Algunos medicamentos pueden interactuar con Cafergot. D&iacute;ga a su m&eacute;dico si toma otros medicamentos, especialmente cualquier de los siguientes:</p><ul><li>Clotrimazol, fluconazol, fluoxetina, fluvoxamina, metronidazol, nefazodona, saquinavir, o zileuton porque los efectos secundarios de Cafergot pueden ser aumentados</li><li>Antif&uacute;ngicos de azol (por ejemplo, itraconazol, ketoconazol, voriconazol), beta-bloqueadores (por ejemplo, propranolol), delavirdina, inhibidores de proteasa de VIH (por ejemplo, delavirdina, indinavir, nelfinavir, ritonavir), efavirenz, los antibi&oacute;ticos ket&oacute;lidos (por ejemplo, telitromicina), antibi&oacute;ticos macr&oacute;lidos (por ejemplo, eritromicina, claritromicina), o agonistas selectivos de 5-HT (por ejemplo, sumatript&aacute;n, eletript&aacute;n), porque el riesgo de efectos secundarios graves, incluyendo latidos irregulares o disminuci&oacute;n de ox&iacute;geno a las extremidades (por ejemplo, manos, pies) o en el cerebro, puede ser aumentado</li><li>Agentes presoras (por ejemplo, norepinefrina) o simpaticomim&eacute;ticos (por ejemplo, pseudoefedrina, albuterol), porque el riesgo de efectos secundarios, incluyendo la presi&oacute;n arterial muy alta, puede ser aumentado</li><li>Quinolonas (por ejemplo, levofloxacina), porque el riesgo de efectos secundarios, tales como nerviosismo, insomnio, latidos cardiacos r&aacute;pidos, puede ser aumentado</li><li>Teofilina porque las acciones y los efectos secundarios pueden ser aumentados por Cafergot.</li></ul><p>No es una lista completa de todas las interacciones que pueden ocurrir.  Pregunte a su m&eacute;dico si Cafergot puede interaccionar con otros  medicamentos que toma. Consulte con su m&eacute;dico antes de iniciar, detener o  cambiar la dosis de cualquier medicamento.</p><p><strong>Informaci&oacute;n importante sobre seguridad: </strong></p><ul><li>No exceda la dosis recomendada o tome Cafergot durante m&aacute;s tiempo que lo recetado sin antes consultar con el m&eacute;dico. Cafergot no es para uso prolongado y diario.</li><li>El uso de nicotina puede aumentar el riesgo de efectos secundarios graves de Cafergot. Consulte con el m&eacute;dico antes de usar Cafergot si usted fuma o usa cualquier otro tipo de nicotina.</li><li>Utilice Cafergot con precauci&oacute;n extrema en los ni&ntilde;os. La seguridad y eficacia no han sido confirmadas.</li><li>Embarazo y lactancia: No use Cafergot si est&aacute; embarazada. Si usted sospecha que podr&iacute;a estar embarazada, consulte con su m&eacute;dico inmediatamente. Cafergot no debe ser tomado durante el parto. Cafergot se excreta en la leche materna. Si usted amamanta o amamantar&aacute; mientras el uso de Cafergot, consulte con su m&eacute;dico o farmac&eacute;utico para discutir los riesgos para su beb&eacute;.</li></ul><p>Cuando es usado durante largos per&iacute;odos de tiempo o en dosis altas, algunas personas desarrollan una necesidad de seguir la toma de Cafergot. Esto es conocido como la dependencia o adicci&oacute;n. Es importante que Usted toma Cafergot seg&uacute;n las instrucciones del m&eacute;dico. Cafergot no es para uso prolongado y diario.</p><p><strong>EFECTOS SECUNDARIOS</strong></p><p>Todos los medicamentos pueden causar efectos secundarios, pero muchas  personas no tienen estos efectos, o tienen efectos secundarios menores.</p><p>Consulte con su m&eacute;dico si cualquier de estos efectos secundarios m&aacute;s comunes persiste o vuelve molesto:</p><p>N&aacute;useas.</p><p>Busque atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica inmediatamente si alguno de estos efectos secundarios graves ocurre:</p><p>Las reacciones al&eacute;rgicas graves (erupci&oacute;n cut&aacute;nea, urticaria, picaz&oacute;n, dificultad para respirar, opresi&oacute;n en el pecho, hinchaz&oacute;n de la boca, cara, labios o lengua), el color azul de los dedos de las manos o pies, dolor o opresi&oacute;n en el pecho, los dedos/dedos de los pies fr&iacute;os o p&aacute;lidos , diarrea, mareos, alucinaciones, dolor de cabeza, latido del coraz&oacute;n irregular, calambres en las piernas o debilidad, cambios mentales o de humor, dolor muscular, entumecimiento o hormigueo en las manos, los pies o la piel, zumbido en los o&iacute;dos, convulsiones, n&aacute;usea severa o persistente o v&oacute;mitos , falta de aliento, hinchaz&oacute;n, latido del coraz&oacute;n r&aacute;pido o lento temporal, v&oacute;mitos, pulso flojo.</p><p>No es una lista completa de efectos secundarios que pueden ocurrir. Si  usted tiene preguntas sobre los efectos secundarios, consulte con el  m&eacute;dico.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:9:"0.6304504";s:9:"pack_name";s:5:"pills";s:4:"type";s:2:"mg";s:7:"analogs";N;s:8:"synonims";a:37:{i:0;s:8:"Wigraine";i:1;s:9:"Trinergot";i:2;s:6:"Theine";i:3;s:9:"Synkapton";i:4;s:8:"Migranil";i:5;s:8:"Migergot";i:6;s:17:"Methyltheobromine";i:7;s:7:"Mateine";i:8;s:9:"Lingraine";i:9;s:20:"Gynergène caféiné";i:10;s:9:"Guaranine";i:11;s:6:"Ericaf";i:12;s:7:"Ergotan";i:13;s:11:"Ergotaminum";i:14;s:10:"Ergotamina";i:15;s:9:"Ergotamin";i:16;s:7:"Ergonex";i:17;s:7:"Ergomar";i:18;s:10:"Ergokoffin";i:19;s:11:"Ergo-kranit";i:20;s:9:"Ergo-caff";i:21;s:5:"Ergam";i:22;s:5:"Ercaf";i:23;s:11:"Coffekapton";i:24;s:9:"Coffeinum";i:25;s:7:"Coffein";i:26;s:9:"Coffecorn";i:27;s:9:"Coffeavet";i:28;s:19:"Caffeine-ergotamine";i:29;s:10:"Caffedrine";i:30;s:9:"Cafetrate";i:31;s:8:"Caféine";i:32;s:8:"Cafeína";i:33;s:6:"Cafcit";i:34;s:8:"Cafatine";i:35;s:9:"Avamigran";i:36;s:7:"Anervan";}s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:100;a:7:{i:2306;a:5:{s:10:"id_pac